These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-1::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: october, december, november, july, august
There are 5 different favourite beverages: lemonade, almond-milk, juice, sprite, hot-chocolate
1. the person who's birthday is in december is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in august##5
5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
7. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person drinking lemonade##5
8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |      3       |    4    |     5      |
| Birthday   | october    | august   | december      | july  | november    |
| Beverage   | lemonade | hot-chocolate | juice | almond-milk | sprite |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-2::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  doctor, scientist, project-manager, social-worker, engineer
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: january, july, june, november, september
 1. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the right of the doctor##5
 2. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in january##5
 3. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in november##5
 4. the project-manager is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##5
 6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
 7. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the scientist##3
 8. the scientist is on the left or right of the project-manager##3
 9. the scientist is in the middle##1
10. the scientist is between the person who's birthday is in november and the person who's birthday is in september##2
11. the doctor is somewhere to the right of the social-worker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |      4      |   5    |
| Job   | social-worker   | doctor     | scientist | project-manager | engineer    |
| Birthday     | july | november | january   | september        | june |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-3::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: grey, white, red, pink, lavender
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: funk, house, electronic, rock, punk
1. the person who likes lavender is in the middle##1
2. the person who likes red is somewhere to the left of the fan of house##5
3. the fan of rock is the person who likes grey##1
4. the fan of house is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
5. the fan of house is the fan of house##1
6. the fan of rock is somewhere to the left of the fan of punk##5
7. the person who likes pink is on the right of the fan of rock##1
8. the fan of funk is between the person who likes white and the person who likes grey##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |
| Color   | red   | white       | lavender         | grey | pink |
| Music-Genre      | electronic | house | funk | rock   | punk |

