.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-4::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, bongani, cain, fonseca, oliveros
5 different games are played: chess, monopoly, backgammon, domino, scrabble
 1. the person playing scrabble is somewhere to the left of the oliveros-smoker##5
 2. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the cain-smoker##3
 3. the fonseca-smoker is the person playing domino##1
 4. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
 5. the person playing domino is the fonseca-smoker##1
 6. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
 7. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
 8. the person playing monopoly is in an even position##4
 9. the oliveros-smoker is in an odd position##4
10. the cain-smoker is somewhere to the left of the oliveros-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |    4     |     5      |
| Cigar   | fonseca     | cain  | oliveros   | bongani      | prince  |
| Game   | domino | scrabble | chess | monopoly | backgammon |

