.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-5::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  mechanic, social-worker, manager, photographer, dancer
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, aristoff, vegafina, pall-mall, baccarat
1. the baccarat-smoker is on the left or right of the mechanic##3
2. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the manager##1
3. the vegafina-smoker is between the dancer and the aristoff-smoker##2
4. the photographer is on the left or right of the dancer##3
5. the davidoff-smoker is somewhere to the left of the manager##5
6. the manager is on the right of the mechanic##1
7. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |   5    |
| Job    | social-worker | mechanic | manager     | photographer     | dancer |
| Cigar   | baccarat  | davidoff   | aristoff | vegafina | pall-mall |

