.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-6::.
5 different games are played: canasta, scrabble, poker, bridge, backgammon
House: cottage, futuristic, art-deco, colonial, craftsman
 1. the person playing scrabble is on the left or right of the person playing bridge##3
 2. the person playing backgammon is in an odd position##4
 3. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the left of the art-deco house##5
 4. the colonial house is somewhere to the left of the cottage house##5
 5. the person playing bridge is somewhere to the right of the craftsman house##5
 6. the colonial house is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the futuristic house is somewhere to the left of the person playing bridge##5
 8. the person playing bridge is on the right of the art-deco house##1
 9. the person playing poker is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
10. the craftsman house is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
11. the person playing poker is somewhere to the left of the person playing canasta##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3      |     4     |    5     |
| Game   | poker | canasta | backgammon  | scrabble     | bridge  |
| House     | colonial    | craftsman    | futuristic | art-deco | cottage |

