.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-7::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, old-henry, bolivar, alhambra, tiparillo
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: iris, balloon-flower, zinnia, daisy, azalea
1. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
2. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
3. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
4. the tiparillo-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##5
5. the alhambra-smoker is the person who growszinnia##1
6. the old-henry-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdaisy##5
7. the person who growsballoon-flower is somewhere to the right of the person who growsiris##5
8. the havana-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who growsiris##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |   2   |   3   |     4     |   5   |
| Cigar      | old-henry | alhambra  | havana | tiparillo  | bolivar |
| Flower   | azalea          | zinnia | daisy | iris | balloon-flower   |

