.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-8::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: sunflower, aconite, zinnia, azalea, amaryllis
The people have 5 different jobs:  electrician, security-guard, nurse, engineer, coach
1. the person who growssunflower is the person who growssunflower##1
2. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the coach##1
3. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
4. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
5. the coach is on the right of the security-guard##1
6. the electrician is somewhere to the right of the person who growszinnia##5
7. the person who growsamaryllis is between the person who growssunflower and the engineer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5     |
| Flower          | zinnia    | aconite    | amaryllis | sunflower | azalea   |
| Job   | nurse | engineer | security-guard | coach  | electrician |

