.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-9::.
City: london, liverpool, hamburg, colone, paris
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: surfing, lacrosse, climbing, sailing, handball
1. the person who's sport is sailing is between the person traveling to hamburg and the person who's sport is handball##2
2. the person traveling to london is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's sport is sailing is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5
4. the person who's sport is sailing is in an odd position##4
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to colone##5
6. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far left##1
7. the person traveling to paris is the person who's sport is sailing##1
8. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |    4    |      5      |
| City      | colone      | hamburg      | paris   | liverpool    | london |
| Sport   | surfing | lacrosse | sailing | handball | climbing   |

