.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-11::.
House: modern, craftsman, victorian, palace, cape-cod
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: drama, adventure, sports, superhero, action
 1. the craftsman house is on the left or right of the palace house##3
 2. the person watching drama movies is in an even position##4
 3. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3
 4. the victorian house is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
 5. the person watching superhero movies is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the victorian house is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
 7. the palace house is somewhere to the right of the modern house##5
 8. the victorian house is somewhere to the right of the person watching action movies##5
 9. the victorian house is between the modern house and the palace house##2
10. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching adventure movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |    4    |    5     |
| House   | cape-cod     | modern       | victorian    | palace | craftsman |
| Movie-Genre      | action | adventure | sports | drama | superhero  |

