.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-12::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: horror, thriller, adventure, fantasy, martial-arts
5 different pets are kept: ferret, fish, cat, rat, frog
1. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5
2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
3. the person watching adventure movies is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the fish is the person watching fantasy movies##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
6. the owner of the fish is between the owner of the ferret and the owner of the frog##2
7. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the ferret##5
8. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
9. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching adventure movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3     |     4     |    5    |
| Movie-Genre          | thriller  | horror  | martial-arts    | fantasy | adventure  |
| Pet   | cat | rat | ferret | fish | frog |

