.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-13::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: azure, amber, emerald, blue, coral
House: futuristic, craftsman, victorian, cape-cod, ranch-style
1. the person who likes blue is between the futuristic house and the person who likes coral##2
2. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the ranch-style house##3
3. the cape-cod house is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who likes azure is on the right of the craftsman house##1
5. the victorian house is somewhere to the left of the ranch-style house##5
6. the person who likes coral is on the left or right of the person who likes blue##3
7. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
8. the ranch-style house is somewhere to the left of the craftsman house##5
9. the craftsman house is on the left or right of the person who likes emerald##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4      |   5    |
| Color    | coral        | blue | emerald | amber   | azure |
| House   | victorian | ranch-style  | futuristic     | craftsman | cape-cod  |

