.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-14::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: fishing, writing, video-games, card-games, filmmaking
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, oliveros, alhambra, bolivar, bongani
1. the bolivar-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##5
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the alhambra-smoker##2
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the right of the bolivar-smoker##5
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left or right of the alhambra-smoker##3
5. the bolivar-smoker is on the left or right of the bongani-smoker##3
6. the bolivar-smoker is in an even position##4
7. the person who's hobby is writing is the bolivar-smoker##1
8. the chaman-smoker is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
9. the oliveros-smoker is between the bolivar-smoker and the person who's hobby is fishing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |    5    |
| Hobby   | card-games | fishing | video-games    | writing | filmmaking  |
| Cigar   | alhambra       | chaman       | oliveros | bolivar  | bongani |

