The people's birthday is in 5 different months: december, september, january, august, may
1. the person playing chess is between the person who's birthday is in may and the person playing snooker##2
2. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
3. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in may##5
4. the person playing poker is on the far right##1
5. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who's birthday is in august##2
6. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in august##5
7. the person who's birthday is in january is in an odd position##4
8. the person playing whist is somewhere to the left of the person playing chess##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3      |      4      |      5      |
| Game   | whist    | chess    | snooker | scrabble     | poker |
| Birthday     | may | december | august    | september | january  |

