There 5 different types of food: cranberry, cucumber, broccoli, kiwi, mango
1. the person who likes ivory is in the middle##1
2. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
3. the person who likes black is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
4. the person eating cranberry is the person who likes lilac##1
5. the person eating kiwi is on the far left##1
6. the person eating mango is the person who likes emerald##1
7. the person who likes emerald is on the far right##1
8. the person who likes ebony is somewhere to the right of the person eating kiwi##5
9. the person eating cranberry is on the left or right of the person eating mango##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3       |     4     |    5    |
| Color         | black  | ebony | ivory | lilac | emerald |
| Food   | kiwi | broccoli   | cucumber   | cranberry | mango |

