1. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person eating lettuce##3
2. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the left of the person eating lettuce##5
3. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person eating broccoli##5
4. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
5. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person drinking coffee##5
6. the person eating lettuce is on the left or right of the person eating cauliflower##3
7. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person eating grapes##3
8. the person eating cauliflower is in an odd position##4
9. the person drinking mirinda is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |    4    |     5      |
| Food         | papaya | grapes | cauliflower   | lettuce | broccoli |
| Beverage   | mirinda       | fanta         | tea | coffee    | almond-milk       |

