.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-5-20::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: writing, collecting, baking, magic-tricks, board-games
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: satire, thriller, drama, time-travel, scientific
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is between the person who's hobby is writing and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
2. the person watching satire movies is between the person watching drama movies and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
4. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching thriller movies##5
5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
6. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |      2       |     3      |      4       |    5     |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks      | board-games     | collecting      | writing       | baking    |
| Movie-Genre        | drama | satire | thriller | scientific | time-travel |

 